export default function About() { return (

About

Hi there! I'm Yamam Jamal, I grew up in Southern California and developed an interest for technology and problem-solving. test DONE?!?!?

I earned my Mechanical Engineering degree from California State University of Fullerton, where I started to gain my analytical and critical thinking skills. After graduating, I decided that my true passion lied within computer science.

I decided to further my education and pursued a post-baccalaureate degree in Computer Science from Oregon State University. This program has allowed to me to pursure my dream of becoming a future software developer.

I hope to one day leverage my background in mechanical engineering and computer science to show case my passion for technology and problem solving by solving real world problems.

The calculator app is to demonstrate my understanding of several different technologies such as React, Javascript, HTML and CSS. I hope you enjoy using the calculator app just as much as I did creating it!

Thanks for visiting the Calculator App!
